method.name: end
method.description: The time the activity will end at, in milliseconds since Unix epoch. The SDK will try to convert seconds to milliseconds if a small-ish value is passed in. If specified, the Discord client will render a countdown timer showing how long until the activity ends.

method.name: start
method.description: The time the activity started, in milliseconds since Unix epoch. The SDK will try to convert seconds to milliseconds if a small-ish value is passed in. If specified, the Discord client will render a count up timer showing how long the user has been playing this activity.
